WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.990
Kur shikon yjet naten

00:00:02.990 --> 00:00:05.426
ajo qe mund te shohesh
eshte e mrekullueshme.

00:00:05.426 --> 00:00:06.696
Eshte e bukur.

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.816
Por, me mahnitese eshte ajo qe nuk shohim,

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.216
sepse nga ato qe dime tani,

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:14.616
rreth yjeve ose pothuajse cdo ylli,

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:15.896
ndodhet nje planet,

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:17.120
ose ndoshta disa.

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:20.216
Pra ajo qe kjo foto nuk po ju tregon

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:22.376
jane te gjithe planetet qe ne dime

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:23.800
qe jane ne hapesire.

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:27.496
Mendojme rreth planeteve per gjera qe jane

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:29.376
shume te ndryshme nga ai i joni.

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.816
Pra ja ku jemi ne nje planet,